PrecisORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (WHITE RIVER FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which provides for (a) the withdrawal from disposal of some 2,211 hectares of land in the Yukon until April 30, 2004, in order to facilitate the settlement of native land claims, and (b) the repeal of a similar Withdrawal from Disposal Order made on June 23, 1999.
